name: Artificial Victorian dreams on clods - Serie 1

metadata.description: On a resurgent clod of earth suspended in the sky, the plot of a dream is woven, a mirage of an elusive Victorian lady, imprisoned in the enchanting garden of her castle. A vision that invites us to reflect: wealth, not always sinuous, dances on the tightrope of freedom.
metadata.name: Feel stuck #1/9
